    "description": "Peel, jump, swap - Embark on a grand sticky adventure with Perin!<br>Help Perin, the protagonist of this story, travel a world plunged into stickery-madness brought upon a witch's mischief in a puzzle-action game depicting their legacy.<br><br>The key to strategy in this game is &quot;how&quot; you interact with the stickers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slow-peel</h2>Bend the stickers to your will by slowly peeling it off from the corners!<br>It might even create new platforms to step on...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d2201f5a88f215e272d8f485a4c7532f.poster.avif?t=1743212843\" width=384 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d2201f5a88f215e272d8f485a4c7532f.webm?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d2201f5a88f215e272d8f485a4c7532f.mp4?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Change the order on how the stickers are placed!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/bbf600a15e38268aa3ff9a2148ce08f2.poster.avif?t=1743212843\" width=384 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/bbf600a15e38268aa3ff9a2148ce08f2.webm?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/bbf600a15e38268aa3ff9a2148ce08f2.mp4?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>By reforming the stickers, maybe the path forward might just unveil themselves..?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power-peel</h2>Rip the stickers off with one swift move by storing power!<br>It might create enough force to do a bigger jump if you're on it..?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d011cd554b97776c57a820a572542453.poster.avif?t=1743212843\" width=384 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d011cd554b97776c57a820a572542453.webm?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/d011cd554b97776c57a820a572542453.mp4?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enemies layered on top won't stand a chance against it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/842f9f729b4419989346239cc56c6d99.poster.avif?t=1743212843\" width=384 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/842f9f729b4419989346239cc56c6d99.webm?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/842f9f729b4419989346239cc56c6d99.mp4?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Estimated total play time</h2>2 and a half hours - 3 hours<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/90aec4e6e2507854e4320d31d80c5741.poster.avif?t=1743212843\" width=384 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/90aec4e6e2507854e4320d31d80c5741.webm?t=1743212843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006350/extras/90aec4e6e2507854e432